Thus, according to the present invention, a method is provided for screening the compounds that have a selective androgen receptor modulatory activity, characterized in comprising the following steps:


(1) a step of adding a test substance to a cultured prostate cancer cell, and measuring the mRNA expression level of prostate-specific antigen (PSA) or the production level of prostate-specific antigen (PSA) in said cultured prostate cancer cell; and,

(2) a step of adding a test substance to a cultured adipocyte, and measuring the mRNA expression level of uncoupling protein 1 (UCP-1) or the production level of uncoupling protein 1 (UCP-1) in said cultured adipocytes;
